summer at stanford university high school and college summer programs skip to content search search home programs international basics need to know about us apply login about us related links about stanford summer session bay area student resources stanford policies contact us home about us about us summer session at stanford university invites students to experience campus life at one of the world's premier universities stanford summer session is open to current stanford university students sophomores juniors seniors and graduate students only students from other colleges and universities in the united states and internationally high school students who demonstrate their readiness for university courses current stanford university students do not need to formally apply for stanford summer session and can simply register for summer courses via axess our unique programs balance challenging academics with educational and social activities to produce a well rounded summer of personal challenge and growth the campus atmosphere is informal year round with hundreds of activities students can engage in bicycling or running in the foothills playing tennis or golf enjoying the stanford summer theater or jazz festival or attending the science lecture series to name just a few learn more about our programs stanford university home map & directions help stanford university summer session terms of use copyright complaints powered by eresources
